title: DAZ3D - Anna HD for Victoria 7
description:
Anna HD for Victoria 7
----------------------
 
https://cdn.pximg.xyz/c6527980f5bfafd34a84248b7b163cb0.jpg

www.daz3d.com/catalog/product/view/id/34143

It is a so easy to lose yourself in her big brown eyes. This is Anna for Victoria 7, a seductive beauty whose skin-tone and special face will work for a variety of settings.
Long hours of work went into the morphs to create a truly unique character. The skin was crafted from high-res photos, no resources were used. The textures are based on the Genesis 3 Female Base UV maps, so the skin will work with every other character. Advanced Iray and 3Delight materials are included
